Description: Made from dry grinding of high quality mature premium selected whole Salem turmeric fingers. It is 100 % natural; it’s free from adulterants, preservatives, artificial colour and flavour. Cool in Cool’s turmeric powder can be used to prepare all variety of dishes, cosmetics and medicinal use.
